# Important Files

- `.cursor/rules/important-files.mdc`: Lists all important files for the project
- `package.json`: NPM package configuration with scripts and dependencies
- `tsconfig.json`: TypeScript configuration
- `src/main.ts`: Main entry point for the MCP server
- `.gitignore`: Specifies intentionally untracked files to ignore

Note: When adding new important files to the project, please add them to this list.